snippet.title: Paw Patrol Sea Patrol Sub Patroller Submarine Hover Vehicle Unboxing || Keith's Toy Box
snippet.description:
PAW Patrol – Sub Patroller
Dive into adventure with the Sea Patrol’s rescue vehicle: the Sub Patroller! Designed to take pups on action-packed rescue missions, the Sub Patroller has all kinds of features for kids to explore! Go from sky to the sea by switching from hover mode to sub mode! Push the yellow button to activate flashing lights and hear sounds from the pups’ sea adventures! Launch the life rings and open the escape hatch so Ryder can swim out to sea and save the day! What treasures will you find at the bottom of Adventure Bay? 

Pups to the rescue! Embark on daring new missions with Ryder and his Sub Patroller! In this incredible rescue vehicle, you can soar through the sky or dive through the imaginary sea! Load Ryder (figure included) into the cockpit and plunge straight into action. Press down on the yellow button to hear Sea Patrol sounds and see headlights flash, lighting your way for deep sea missions. When you and Ryder spot a sea friend in trouble, use the life ring launcher! Press down on the yellow periscope to hear sounds, see flashing lights and launch life rings to save the day! If the mission takes you into a tiny space, Ryder can go from driver to diver! Open the trapdoor and he’ll swim to adventure using his handheld propeller. As the Paw Patrol’s incredible rescue vehicle, there’s room for pups on board! Fly to shore and load the pups into the cargo bay and cockpit! No mission is too big – especially with the Sub Patroller! Climb on board and deep dive into adventure!

snippet.title: 2018 McDONALD'S INCREDIBLES 2 HAPPY MEAL TOYS DISNEY PIXAR MOVIE FULL SET 10 KIDS TOY UNBOXING WORLD
snippet.description:
2018 New Next McDonald's Incredibles 2 Happy Meal toys Disney Pixar movie full set of 10 kids meal toys world collection toy unboxing review by Fast Food Toys. Fast Food Toys reviews the 2018 McDonalds Incredibles 2 movie Happy Meal toys coming up in June and July 2018. The Disney Pixar Incredibles 2 movie follows up after the Incredibles movie in 2004. McD's US has 10 Incredibles 2 toys. The next toys will be the McDonalds Hotel Transylvania 3 Happy Meal toys after the McDonalds Incredibles toys and Hasbro Gaming Happy Meal toys. We've already done the unboxing of the McDonald's Incredibles 2 Happy Meal toys and review them unboxed. Both McDonald's UK & Canada have the 2018 McDonalds Super Mario Happy Meal toys next after their respective Justice League Action & the Amazing World Of Gumball Happy Meal toys. Disney and McD's have announced they are back together after 12 years apart since 2006. McDonald's Incredibles Happy Meal toys are known worldwide. In Brazil they are known as mclanche feliz brinquedos Os Incríveis 2 while in Mexico they are cajita feliz juguetes los increíbles 2. We love the Incredibles 2 movie trailers and the McDonald's Incredibles 2 Happy Meal toys commercial advert! They will also have the McDonalds Disney Ralph Breaks the Internet: Wreck-It Ralph 2 movie Happy Meal toys in November 2018! Some McD's Europe & Asia will have the 2018 McDonalds My Little Pony and Transformers Happy Meal toys next! The US full set of 10 McDonalds Incredibles 2 toys include: #1 Mr Incredible #2 Elasticycle #3 Dash Parr #4 Violet #5 Levitating Jack-Jack #6 Frozone #7 Mrs. Incredible a.k.a. Elastigirl #8 Raccoon Surprise #9 Edna Mode #10 Wind-Up Jack-Jack.

snippet.title: LEGO Friends Funny Octopus Ride (41373) - Toy Unboxing and Speed Build
snippet.description:
Funny Octopus Ride

Item: 41373
Ages: 7+
Pieces: 324

Transport your youngster to the excitement of the amusement pier on the LEGO® Friends 41373 Funny Octopus Ride. Kids will love recreating the thrill of a fairground ride with this LEGO Friends set. It features an octopus body and at the end of its tentacles are 4 cars shaped like cute sea creatures. By turning the octopus's top hat, the cars fly up and down, and round and round. Included is a buildable carnival ticket booth that also sells popcorn and helps to encourage imaginative play. Give any LEGO builder an amazing building experience with Instructions PLUS, available in the LEGO Life app for smartphones and tablets. The easy-to-use, intuitive building instructions let them zoom, rotate and visualize their creation using the special ghost mode as they go. Instructions PLUS is also great for younger builders, guiding them through the building process for a greater sense of independence and achievement. This amusement park playset includes 2 mini-doll figures, plus a bird figure.

- Amusement park set includes 2 mini-doll figures: Andrea and Ethan, plus a bird figure.
- Features an octopus fairground ride with a spinning function, 4 cars shaped like sea creatures and a kiosk.
- Amusement park toy accessory elements include sunglasses, camera, ticket and popcorn.
- Octopus's hat has a twisting function that allows the cars to fly round.
- Kids can pretend to be Andrea, taking some action shots of Ethan on the ride.
- Combine with 41375 Heartlake City Amusement Pier and 41337 Underwater Loop to extend the funfair play.
- Use the LEGO® Life app to access the intuitive Instructions PLUS building instructions. Help even younger builders through the building process, with easy-to-use zoom, rotate and ghost-mode functions to visualize their creations as they go.
- LEGO® Friends playsets encourage imaginative play, and make building creative and fun.
- This octopus carnival ride makes an ideal Christmas gift or gift for the holiday season for creative kids.
- This set is part of the LEGO® Friends world of everyday heroes and exciting real-world scenarios.
- Amusement park toy set measures over 7” (18cm) high, 10” (27cm) wide and 9” (24cm) deep.

Product description: This unique snap-together fashion kit comes with 260 pieces of funny jewelry beads in various shapes, sizes, designs, colors. Stimulate creativity Skills Do it by yourselves, make a beautiful decoration and puts you in a good happy mood. Girls snap the beads cultivate their hand-eye cooperation skill. Best gift for girls beading and jewelry making,also a good idea for birthday and Chritsmas gift.
Review by Davna (mom)- Once I received this DIY jewelry making kit I first looked at the packaging and I really like that it came in a plastic jar container that is really easy to open and close for Tiffany. The beads themselves are actually very well made, the quality  feels like beads that you would find at the Lakeshore Learning Store (except for HALF the price!) I love that the beads come in different textures, sizes and vibrant colors. It comes with a little booklet with pictures of some of the jewelry you can create which Tiffany liked to look at and recreated some of those accessories. The main thing I love about this toy is that it actually keeps both my girls entertained for LONG periods of time and it allows for their creativity to shine. We also use these to do some math, count and even create patterns! This is NOT meant for children under 3 as there are many small chocking hazard pieces BUT my youngest enjoys playing with them too under my CAREFUL supervision. It has been over a week now since we received this toy and since then both my girls have been playing with them DAILY! I highly recommend! 
CONS- The only con I found about this product is that some beads are harder to connect than others. PAW Patrol – Sub Patroller
Dive into adventure with the Sea Patrol’s rescue vehicle: the Sub Patroller! Designed to take pups on action-packed rescue missions, the Sub Patroller has all kinds of features for kids to explore! Go from sky to the sea by switching from hover mode to sub mode! Push the yellow button to activate flashing lights and hear sounds from the pups’ sea adventures! Launch the life rings and open the escape hatch so Ryder can swim out to sea and save the day! What treasures will you find at the bottom of Adventure Bay? 

Pups to the rescue! Embark on daring new missions with Ryder and his Sub Patroller! In this incredible rescue vehicle, you can soar through the sky or dive through the imaginary sea! Load Ryder (figure included) into the cockpit and plunge straight into action. Press down on the yellow button to hear Sea Patrol sounds and see headlights flash, lighting your way for deep sea missions. When you and Ryder spot a sea friend in trouble, use the life ring launcher! Press down on the yellow periscope to hear sounds, see flashing lights and launch life rings to save the day! If the mission takes you into a tiny space, Ryder can go from driver to diver! Open the trapdoor and he’ll swim to adventure using his handheld propeller. As the Paw Patrol’s incredible rescue vehicle, there’s room for pups on board! Fly to shore and load the pups into the cargo bay and cockpit! No mission is too big – especially with the Sub Patroller! Climb on board and deep dive into adventure!

snippet.title: LEGO Friends Funny Octopus Ride (41373) - Toy Unboxing and Speed Build
snippet.description:
Funny Octopus Ride

Item: 41373
Ages: 7+
Pieces: 324

Transport your youngster to the excitement of the amusement pier on the LEGO® Friends 41373 Funny Octopus Ride. Kids will love recreating the thrill of a fairground ride with this LEGO Friends set. It features an octopus body and at the end of its tentacles are 4 cars shaped like cute sea creatures. By turning the octopus's top hat, the cars fly up and down, and round and round. Included is a buildable carnival ticket booth that also sells popcorn and helps to encourage imaginative play. Give any LEGO builder an amazing building experience with Instructions PLUS, available in the LEGO Life app for smartphones and tablets. The easy-to-use, intuitive building instructions let them zoom, rotate and visualize their creation using the special ghost mode as they go. Instructions PLUS is also great for younger builders, guiding them through the building process for a greater sense of independence and achievement. This amusement park playset includes 2 mini-doll figures, plus a bird figure.

- Amusement park set includes 2 mini-doll figures: Andrea and Ethan, plus a bird figure.
- Features an octopus fairground ride with a spinning function, 4 cars shaped like sea creatures and a kiosk.
- Amusement park toy accessory elements include sunglasses, camera, ticket and popcorn.
- Octopus's hat has a twisting function that allows the cars to fly round.
- Kids can pretend to be Andrea, taking some action shots of Ethan on the ride.
- Combine with 41375 Heartlake City Amusement Pier and 41337 Underwater Loop to extend the funfair play.
- Use the LEGO® Life app to access the intuitive Instructions PLUS building instructions. Help even younger builders through the building process, with easy-to-use zoom, rotate and ghost-mode functions to visualize their creations as they go.
- LEGO® Friends playsets encourage imaginative play, and make building creative and fun.
- This octopus carnival ride makes an ideal Christmas gift or gift for the holiday season for creative kids.
- This set is part of the LEGO® Friends world of everyday heroes and exciting real-world scenarios.
- Amusement park toy set measures over 7” (18cm) high, 10” (27cm) wide and 9” (24cm) deep.

The Disney Junior Mickey Mouse Clubhouse Doctor Kit is a way for your Mickey Mouse Fan into a doctor. There are similar Disney Junior Doc McStuffins Doctor kits, but this one is definitely designed for a Mickey Mouse fan.

Notes-

- Comes with a battery operated stethoscope. The stethoscope is probably the highlight of the set.

- Has a thermometer for checking temperature - each time you click the thermometer you change the temperature on its display.

- A small flashlight is included for checking throats and ears

- The blood pressure cuff doesn't pump with air.... unlike the one that comes with the Doc mcStuffins playset

- Has a small mirror

- A few other items are included like two band aids

Final Verdict - Our daughter prefers the Mickey Mouse Clubhouse Doctor kit over-and-above the one from Doc McStuffins. She prefers the blood pressure cuff from Doc McStuffins but she likes all of the additional doctor tools in the Mickey kit.
